{"tid":1351093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［整合] 7.21上環開槍清場 有片有圖！【幫COPY POST】","createTime":"2019-07-22T14:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T23:51:28.000Z","uid":94771,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"73df434b010ae9eb073c24373b90a8c0318bccbf","tid":1351093,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:34:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7.21上環警察暴力清場 開左最少36槍啊！</span></span>對於開槍我地唔可以慣！如果香港人連開槍都可以習慣，可以冇感覺，咁今次真係仆街喇！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲有，呢個暴力清場同元朗鄉黑圍毆市民係同時間發生！<br />\n警察係利用元朗事件遮蓋/掩飾開槍事件！</span></span><br />\nCredit to: <a href=\"https://t.me/c/1128741080/106975\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1128741080%2F106975&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=13b4dc04\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1128741080/106975</a> 有上環元朗並列時序<br />\n<br />\n上環暴力清場重點整合<br />\n<br />\n● 警察於無預警下開槍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G4tvFOo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG4tvFOo.png&h=61084d53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n● 當時示威者無任何衝擊 正在撒離<br />\n● 水平朝頭發射橡膠子彈<br />\n● 有示威者被擊中頭部 血流不止<br />\n● 警察向示威者開至少36發橡膠子彈<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1RXzfT1aMNU&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR1a_rNq7oOiMOSsjybQI3mWK7A9chioEGMcuzL_IxyFm1eKNXLn1N1nPtI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1RXzfT1aMNU%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26fbclid%3DIwAR1a_rNq7oOiMOSsjybQI3mWK7A9chioEGMcuzL_IxyFm1eKNXLn1N1nPtI&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=bac32f70\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1RXzfT1aMNU&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR1a_rNq7oOiMOSsjybQI3mWK7A9chioEGMcuzL_IxyFm1eKNXLn1N1nPtI</a><br />\n\t （首1&rsquo;23）<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/A9aq3xgaQwk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FA9aq3xgaQwk&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=c0a6a4dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/A9aq3xgaQwk</a><br />\n\t （黑警開槍實錄）<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190721/59847817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190721%2F59847817&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=f4ef134a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190721%2F59847817&h=aa6ab93c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190721/59847817</a> （記者都中彈）<br />\n22:08 上環警察出黑旗。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200954406608272/posts/2326284724075219?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200954406608272%2Fposts%2F2326284724075219%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=c0e08e82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200954406608272/posts/2326284724075219?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n22:20 上環警察發出多枚催淚彈。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2319958694756404?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2319958694756404%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=18e9dc31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2319958694756404?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n22:20 上環警察開槍發射胡椒彈球槍。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863714052448?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10157863714052448%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=f5cac747\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863714052448?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n22:44-46左右，正在撤退之示威人士連續開槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3091637707530089?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F207097505984138%2Fposts%2F3091637707530089%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=5f0c72fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3091637707530089?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/inmediahknet/3332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet%2F3332&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=fae8fab8\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/inmediahknet/3332</a><br />\n<br />\n23:10 上環警方此時才舉起橙旗，警告示威者若再衝擊防線，就會開槍。<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/now.comNews/videos/909622622723938?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnow.comNews%2Fvideos%2F909622622723938%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=98a88ea7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/now.comNews/videos/909622622723938?sfns=mo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n23:42 上環出現槍聲，有示威者倒地，需進行急救<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F2433207320290299%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=e4b6bd3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299?sfns=mo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n● 曾偷偷在天橋上向下對示威者射擊<br />\n2051 有警員在橋上向下邊示威者射橡膠彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvKKLfo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvKKLfo.png&h=87369a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2235 干諾道西 防暴於天橋裝上子彈 #有線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uVW5uHh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVW5uHh.png&h=887a8952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n● 曾衝入群對人發射　<br />\n2245 干諾道西 有持槍警察衝向人群。#立場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O6g9bVM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO6g9bVM.png&h=f1bd06a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/305868249479813/posts/2367755166624434?s=100003182821690&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F305868249479813%2Fposts%2F2367755166624434%3Fs%3D100003182821690%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=c4753a8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/305868249479813/posts/2367755166624434?s=100003182821690&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n● 連續發射催淚彈逾2小時<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MaB1Nui.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMaB1Nui.png&h=cd5a8f1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0hzVRV7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0hzVRV7.png&h=bad2bb5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2319958694756404?s=556534484&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2319958694756404%3Fs%3D556534484%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=a4f91a8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2319958694756404?s=556534484&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n● 警方施放催淚彈後，現場煙霧瀰漫，防暴警察更在濃煙中用警棍毆打示威者。<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkpusupresscom/videos/352141908789716?s=556534484&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkpusupresscom%2Fvideos%2F352141908789716%3Fs%3D556534484%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=5032b7aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkpusupresscom/videos/352141908789716?s=556534484&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n23:00左右，警察多次發放催淚彈，更於濃煙中發射橡膠子彈及布袋彈<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/l7VHf1aEq1Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fl7VHf1aEq1Y&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=6f0bbf3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/l7VHf1aEq1Y</a><br />\n\t （請於1小時46分左右開始觀看）<br />\n<br />\n● 有示威者站在警方防線前，在沒有作出任何攻擊下突然被警察拉走，警察更阻止記者上前拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkpusupresscom/videos/501500607263186/?hc_ref=ARSSF-p33l7GsH8uf1j7M9orPidkDwDzibPEue3sZeLNrl40IshEaP4tG3503GUNqLY&amp;fref=nf&amp;__tn__=kC-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkpusupresscom%2Fvideos%2F501500607263186%2F%3Fhc_ref%3DARSSF-p33l7GsH8uf1j7M9orPidkDwDzibPEue3sZeLNrl40IshEaP4tG3503GUNqLY%26fref%3Dnf%26__tn__%3DkC-R&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=c290114d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkpusupresscom/videos/501500607263186/?hc_ref=ARSSF-p33l7GsH8uf1j7M9orPidkDwDzibPEue3sZeLNrl40IshEaP4tG3503GUNqLY&amp;fref=nf&amp;__tn__=kC-R</a><br />\n\t<br />\n&amp;nbsp;<br />\n警察阻擋記者拍攝<br />\n● 大量施放催淚彈，令街上偏佈煙霧才開槍<br />\n● 全程開大強光燈，直射記者鏡頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1343339/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1343339/page/1</a><br />\n● 警察用催淚彈直射向記者　<br />\n2246 有記者右上臂俾催淚彈殻打中<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcTeVHAuMLP4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn25uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=b3886dca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">網上對上環事件既報導係少之又少！封鎖新聞可恥！</span></span>"},{"pid":"40e2e83067844389a5954e1a0fc31a0f01daca32","tid":1351093,"uid":224323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:36:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92e0fbe2c1ac7bd755b9051f04f2c40773fc1da1","tid":1351093,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:40:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9d29d4a3003d394be79fcd6973045332ec66238","tid":1351093,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:41:43.000Z","msg":"推，兩邊同樣重要！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">721 警黑之夜 - 整合 (上環 + 元朗)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［721上環影片/圖片集結post]屌你上環都好撚重要！！！文宣組入黎幫手推！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1349459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1349459</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[緊急] 上環義士受傷狀況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347981</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［整合] 7.21上環開槍清場 有片有圖！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348209</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n元朗 黑黑相衛 罪狀List，黑材料基地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347791</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兩單野係一個局黎，想spin走上環單野！我地要雙軌並行！</span><br />\n721體現警黑合作，香港政權真面目。<br />\n黑警港島三十幾槍，黑社會元朗亂打人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">光復香港，時代革命！\n\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 八大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre>"},{"pid":"35c9c8b6dcef8d7758ab6a10dc3c7b12eebb7ea2","tid":1351093,"uid":145694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:52:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91aa0b7e61b0c0e0c7abbfadd2511ab098cc6e98","tid":1351093,"uid":152085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:53:22.000Z","msg":"一推再推"},{"pid":"970193729464d12dd650bc92e402ac